# Audio samples are NOT committed to the repository.
# Most sources we work with are CC BY-ND or other licenses where
# bundling derived/extracted clips in a public repo is ambiguous.
#
# Each user fetches samples locally via tools/fetch_speech.sh.
# See examples/CREDITS.md for the canonical commands per sample.
*.wav
*.mp3
*.mp4
*.m4a
*.ogg
*.flac
